headline: Domino's® New Craveable Brand Refresh Makes You Say "Mmm"
summary: Domino's Pizza Inc. (Nasdaq: DPZ) is launching its first brand refresh in 13 years, with the goal of making every aspect of the brand as craveable as what's inside the box. The brand took inspiration from its past and present, and transformed it into modernized elements that will better reach current and future pizza lovers. thumbnail.caption: Domino's is launching a brand refresh with brighter colors, a new font, bold packaging, new team member gear and for the first time ever, a jingle - "Dommmino's" - recorded by five-time GRAMMY® nominated singer-songwriter Shaboozey.
